And after almost two decades at Barcelona will Messi, 33, considered one of the greatest football players, and who calls the club “my life”, leave for new pastures? It would mark the beginning of a new era for the Catalan club.Finally, and on a personal level, I intend to tackle several low level intensity 100km cycling sessions. Will I?Only 2021 will tell. Even though top scientists always had an idea that a pandemic would hit the world at some point in the future, none predicted it would be in 2020.
The Covid-19 pandemic completely decimated the sporting calendar that is only just slowly limping back to normalcy.
Will spectators return to sports in 2021 after their eerie absence in that bizarre 2020 season?



