Kenya-born Briton Chris Froome returned to the peloton last year after recovering from a horrific cycling accident a year earlier. He has publicly stated his desire to win a record equaling fifth Tour de France title. Will it be this year as age catches up with him?
And after almost two decades at Barcelona will Messi, 33, considered one of the greatest football players, and who calls the club “my life”, leave for new pastures? It would mark the beginning of a new era for the Catalan club.
Finally, and on a personal level, I intend to tackle several low level intensity 100km cycling sessions. Will I?
Only 2021 will tell.
